defaultLocation.description: Optional. The default BigQuery location to use. Defaults to "US". See the BigQuery docs for a full list of locations: https://cloud.google.com/bigquery/docs/locations.

databaseSuffix.description: Optional. The suffix that should be appended to all database (Google Cloud project ID) names.

assertionSchema.description: Optional. The default schema (BigQuery dataset ID) for assertions.

defaultSchema.description: Optional. The default schema (BigQuery dataset ID).

defaultDatabase.description: Optional. The default database (Google Cloud project ID).

vars.description: Optional. User-defined variables that are made available to project code during compilation.

transitiveDependenciesIncluded.description: Optional. When set to true, transitive dependencies of included actions will be executed.

fullyRefreshIncrementalTablesEnabled.description: Optional. When set to true, any incremental tables will be fully refreshed.

includedTags.description: Optional. The set of tags to include.

transitiveDependentsIncluded.description: Optional. When set to true, transitive dependents of included actions will be executed.

includedTargets.description: Optional. The set of action identifiers to include.

InvocationConfig.description: Includes various configuration options for a workflow invocation. If both `included_targets` and `included_tags` are unset, all actions will be included.

stack.description: Output only. The error's full stack trace.

path.description: Output only. The path of the file where this error occurred, if available, relative to the project root.

message.description: Output only. The error's top level message.

actionTarget.description: Output only. The identifier of the action where this error occurred, if available.

CompilationError.description: An error encountered when attempting to compile a Dataform project.

unreachable.description: Locations which could not be reached.

nextPageToken.description: A token which can be sent as `page_token` to retrieve the next page. If this field is omitted, there are no subsequent pages.

path.description: Required. The file's full path including filename, relative to the workspace root.

author.description: Required. The author of any merge commit which may be created as a result of merging fetched Git commits into this workspace.

remoteBranch.description: Optional. The name of the branch in the Git remote from which to pull commits. If left unset, the repository's default branch name will be used.

CompilationResultAction.description: Represents a single Dataform action in a compilation result.

canonicalTarget.description: The action's identifier if the project had been compiled without any overrides configured. Unique within the compilation result.

filePath.description: The full path including filename in which this action is located, relative to the workspace root.

assertion.description: The assertion executed by this action.

declaration.description: The declaration declared by this action.

relation.description: The database relation created/updated by this action.

target.description: This action's identifier. Unique within the compilation result.

operations.description: The database operations executed by this action.
